## 🌐 시스템 배포 (Production)

### 3.1 Server 배포 (선택사항)

BR-AIOpsFL을 실제 AIOps 환경에 배포하려면:

```bash
# 1. Docker 이미지 생성
cat > Dockerfile << 'EOF'
FROM python:3.8-slim

WORKDIR /app

# 의존성 설치
RUN pip install --no-cache-dir numpy scikit-learn

# 코드 복사
COPY code/ /app/code/
COPY experiments/ /app/experiments/

# 권한 설정
RUN chmod +x /app/code/*.py

# 기본 실행
CMD ["python", "code/university_v16_BYZANTINE_RESILIENT_FL.py"]
EOF

# 2. Docker 이미지 빌드
docker build -t br-aiopself:latest .

# 3. Docker 컨테이너 실행
docker run -d \
  --name br-aiopself \
  -v $(pwd)/experiments/results:/app/experiments/results \
  br-aiopself:latest

# 4. 컨테이너 상태 확인
docker ps
docker logs br-aiopself
```

### 3.2 Kubernetes 배포 (고급)

```yaml
# k8s-deployment.yaml
apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: br-aiopself
  labels:
    app: br-aiopself
spec:
  replicas: 3
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: br-aiopself
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: br-aiopself
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: br-aiopself
        image: br-aiopself:latest
        resources:
          limits:
            cpu: "2"
            memory: "2Gi"
          requests:
            cpu: "1"
            memory: "1Gi"
        volumeMounts:
        - name: results
          mountPath: /app/experiments/results
      volumes:
      - name: results
        persistentVolumeClaim:
          claimName: br-aiopself-pvc
---
apiVersion: v1
kind: Service
metadata:
  name: br-aiopself-service
spec:
  selector:
    app: br-aiopself
  type: ClusterIP
  ports:
  - protocol: TCP
    port: 8080
    targetPort: 8080
```

배포:
```bash
kubectl apply -f k8s-deployment.yaml
```

