### 4.2 성능 모니터링

```python
# monitoring.py
import psutil
import time

def monitor_system():
    """시스템 성능 모니터링"""
    while True:
        cpu = psutil.cpu_percent(interval=1)
        mem = psutil.virtual_memory().percent

        print(f"CPU: {cpu}%, Memory: {mem}%")

        if cpu > 80 or mem > 80:
            print("⚠️ WARNING: High resource usage")

        time.sleep(60)

if __name__ == "__main__":
    monitor_system()
```

### 4.3 CI/CD 파이프라인

GitHub Actions (`.github/workflows/deploy.yml`):

```yaml
name: Deploy BR-AIOpsFL

on:
  push:
    branches: [master]

jobs:
  test:
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
    steps:
    - uses: actions/checkout@v2
    - uses: actions/setup-python@v2
      with:
        python-version: '3.8'
    - run: pip install -r requirements.txt
    - run: pytest code/test_v16_byzantine_resilient_fl.py -v

  deploy:
    needs: test
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
    steps:
    - uses: actions/checkout@v2
    - run: docker build -t br-aiopself:latest .
    - run: docker push br-aiopself:latest
    - run: kubectl apply -f k8s-deployment.yaml
```

